{"tid":1969510,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"對香港已經死心，光復香港無望，我決定移民","createTime":"2020-04-12T12:54:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T19:20:43.000Z","uid":236368,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d5cc4ff2436006634726f20a7ef17b657ca064df","tid":1969510,"uid":236368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T12:54:45.000Z","msg":"二百萬黃絲根本係笑話，我諗有一百萬以上係港豬，日日出去玩、出去食飯開P，咁嘅智慧仲想香港可以光復？未光復已經中武漢肺炎死咗一大半啦<br />\n<br />\n人地藍絲都知驚，極少出街，自稱黃絲嘅港豬們就爭住中肺炎死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要我同呢班人生活係同一個死方，除咗移民根本冇得揀<br />\n<br />\n加上俾麵神同馬化雲燈走咗一大嚿錢，真係要趁仲有錢有命前逃亡去外國，來生不做香港人"},{"pid":"05b376de6d517e2faff6f96f35ef84ddcb7e4d0f","tid":1969510,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T12:55:40.000Z","msg":"走囉bye~"},{"pid":"ef2fbf8d9e15eb148e1d78078169c9f458e82c2c","tid":1969510,"uid":236368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05b376de6d517e2faff6f96f35ef84ddcb7e4d0f","tid":1969510,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T12:55:40.000Z","msg":"走囉bye~"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T12:59:48.000Z","msg":"再見啦港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7581fd89954584edbfced455196c3a1270c22ba","tid":1969510,"uid":350071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T13:05:14.000Z","msg":"而家先走 樓主一定係窮撚"},{"pid":"791a051a4fcf9bbb32ee4e2acc149fc90ca977ef","tid":1969510,"uid":236368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7581fd89954584edbfced455196c3a1270c22ba","tid":1969510,"uid":350071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T13:05:14.000Z","msg":"而家先走 樓主一定係窮撚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T14:01:02.000Z","msg":"俾你發現咗"},{"pid":"973bf8066072fbcd4a5e7fd0f1a10ab2d2b08b86","tid":1969510,"uid":260023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5cc4ff2436006634726f20a7ef17b657ca064df","tid":1969510,"uid":236368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s